99/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1919", "dates": ["[1919 TO 1934]"], "description": ["Daily (except Sunday), June 1-September 15, 1934 Began with November 1, 1919 issue; ceased with September 15, 1934 issue. Publisher: Nome Publishing Company, <November 8, 1919>. \"Independent.\" Cf. Ayer, 1934. Description based on: Volume 27, No. 39 (September 26, 1925); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 22, 2021). Latest issue consulted: Volume 35, No. 114 (September 15, 1934) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 22, 2021). Nome daily nugget (Nome, Alaska : 1934) 2771-2400 (DLC) 2021270900 (OCoLC)1290313167"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:01.956Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2021270899/", "image_url": [], "index": 7, "language": ["english"], "location": ["nome", "alaska", "united states"], "number": ["online resource", "2021270900", "1289860986", "2021270899", "2771-2249", "2023270637", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the nome nugget (nome, alaska) 1919-1934 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 33.65606, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "nome", "nome (alaska)", "united states", "alaska"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:03:28.349Z", "title": "The Nome nugget", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2021270899/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2021270900/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1934", "dates": ["[1934 TO 1938]"], "description": ["Daily (except Sun.) Began with volume 35, no. 115 (Nov. 8, 1934); print ceased with vol. 39, no. 1 (Jan. 3, 1938). \"Independent.\" Cf. Ayer, 1937. Suspended Sept. 17-Nov. 7, 1934. Volume 35, No. 115 (Nov. 8, 1934); title from masthead (Chroniclinga